('77kuaIpz', 'SandBox', 'When I was just a baby, a woman came to my father''s hall, a woman who was said to be able to speak to the Otherworld. When she saw me, she told him that she saw the mark of the faeries upon me. She performed a divination, and said she had learned that I was to be a prank played on mankind: I should grow up to be a great beauty, but that any man who resolves to marry me shall die.'),
