('7AYJ3SjK', 'SandBox', 'Your family arranged for you to accompany a chieftain of your people. You were not given major responsibilities - mostly carrying messages and tending to his horse -- but it did give you a chance to see how campaigns were planned and men were deployed in battle.'),
