('7HvtT8bm', 'Native', 'Wrought Iron'),
('7hx2Nlmd', 'SandBox', 'Tannery'),
('7HzwCQld', 'SandBox', 'Penton Neretzes was once considered one of the rising stars of the Empire, winning a number of battles against the Aserai and the Vlandians. He is best known, however, for having taken two of the Empire''s last professional legions into the Battanians woods, and losing them in an ambush. He has tried to blame others for the defeat, including the then-emperor Arenicos and his lieutenant, Garios, but the stigma of the defeat has stuck with him. In the civil war he supported Lucon as emperor, though more out of his hatred for Garios and Rhagaea then from any belief in Lucon''s legalistic principles.'),
('7IqpjCDY', 'Native', 'Executing a prisoner will negatively affect your reputation and will decrease your relation with the prisoner''s faction/clan.{newline}You will not be able to undo this action.{newline}Are you sure you want to execute this character?'),
('7IxFrati', 'SandBox', 'Greetings my {?PLAYER.GENDER}lady{?}lord{\?}, how may I help you?'),
('7J9KNFTz', 'SandBox', 'Donate troops to garrison'),
('7j9uHxLM', 'SandBox', 'Current Rank Effect'),
('7jBroUUQ', 'SandBox', 'Your family had little land of their own, so they earned their living from the woods, hunting and trapping. They taught you from an early age that skills like finding game trails and killing an animal with one shot could make the difference between eating and starvation.'),
('7Jd3g0XP', 'SandBoxCore', 'Isilflaed'),
('7jH0kuof', 'SandBoxCore', 'Spiked Mace'),
('7JjctWr3', 'Native', 'Knightly Hammer Shaped Engraved Guard'),
('7JMaPpkN', 'SandBox', 'We built a great temple in the back country, out in the bush, called it the Kingdom of Truth. We whipped two imperial detachments sent to track us down. But Ladicos died, ''Called up to Heaven'' he said on his deathbed, and then we lost our way a bit. We needed food and we needed money, so our chiefs started collecting ''taxes'' from the villages below. Some started taking money from lords and merchants for protection of caravans. And those who grumbled - well, they started turning up dead in the dry streambeds.'),
('7JpAR59k', 'Native', 'Used for carrying goods'),
('7JU1P9lk', 'SandBox', 'Why should I support {s44}?'),
('7Jwuax4w', 'SandBox', 'Extra HP'),
('7JZPTbxB', 'SandBoxCore', 'Scholar'),
('7K13R6SV', 'SandBox', 'You should rest for a while and let your wounds heal.'),
('7k9izAvC', 'SandBox', 'Skolderbrotva'),
('7kALTmxP', 'SandBox', '{FIRST_NAME} of the Lamp'),
('7kc3BHDz', 'SandBox', 'My lady, I would like to dedicate my successes in this recent tournament to you'),
('7kGGgkro', 'SandBox', 'Caravans are 30% cheaper to build. 10% less trade penalty.'),
('7kGwP1Lf', 'SandBox', '{NAME} of the Desert'),
('7kH1W04c', 'SandBox', '{FIRST_NAME} the Anvil'),
('7kMLQcAd', 'SandBox', '{FIRSTNAME} the Dateseller'),
('7kn4Jmdl', 'SandBox', 'Ah, yes! We had such rhymes when I was young.'),
('7kNxogN8', 'SandBox', 'appointing independent elders to uphold the law'),
('7KshRCtM', 'SandBox', 'Excellent. I''ll have the goods delivered to you right away.'),
('7kuFaqzN', 'SandBox', 'However, we can''t organize this like one of those nice arena bouts, where everyone places their bets beforehand. People will walk in, drawn by the noise, and put a denar or two on whichever one of your two they think is winning. I''ll give ''em even odds -- anything else is going to be too tricky for someone who''s already on his third flagon of ale.'),
('7KUO2swN', 'SandBox', 'He really did swing at me first - I think. I was drunk. I know you think I''m just saying that to save my neck, but it''s true. And if a trial by combat affirms that I''m talking truth, than I can get off with a fine, and not swing for what I did.'),
('7LaefhBV', 'SandBoxCore', 'Battania Gear Dummy'),
('7lb73utt', 'Native', 'Grants Strong Arrows, deals more damage.'),
('7ldEMGn6', 'SandBox', 'I don''t like running away from a battle like that.'),
('7ldw4b20', 'SandBox', 'Good. I will be escorting them soon.'),
('7lee0h29', 'SandBox', 'One thing - if one or two die, that''s the fortunes of war, things could go even worse if we get raided and have no one who can fight back... But try not to get them all massacred. These men will take some risks for me, but not have their lives thrown away to no purpose.'),
('7lg12a57', 'SandBox', 'the Brave'),
('7Lkbtnet', 'SandBoxCore', 'Luvina'),
('7llkDelg', 'Native', 'Kingdom Decisions'),
('7llUzJBa', 'SandBox', 'Mercy! Please don''t kill me!'),
('7LmUe8fQ', 'Native', 'Menavlion'),
('7LmUe8fQ', 'Native', 'Menavlion'),
('7LmUe8fQ', 'SandBoxCore', 'Menavlion'),
('7lRnhAgf', 'Native', 'Northern Hourglass Two Handed Grip'),
('7lslkFJx', 'SandBox', 'I like your spirit! Go and bring me one of our enemies, and I''ll toast your name in my hall when you return! And reward you for your efforts, of course...'),
('7lvexPjZ', 'Native', 'Plain'),
('7lWtkqHv', 'SandBox', 'I''ll remember your name.'),
('7mCcppC1', 'SandBox', 'WoodsScoutSkills'),
('7MkoLtWC', 'Native', 'Axe'),
('7MkoLtWC', 'Native', 'Axe'),
('7mnbJz6L', 'SandBox', 'Well, it''s not as simple as all that. Blunt weapons don''t do as much damage as sharp ones, so they won''t bring your enemies down as quickly. And trust me, given the chance, most of the scum you run across would just as soon kill you as look at you, so don''t expect any courtesy when you pull out a club instead of a sword. Moreover, having to drag prisoners to and fro will slow down your party, which is why some people simply set their prisoners free after the fighting''s done. It''s madness. How could anyone turn down all that silver, eh?'),
('7MpWM3y3', 'SandBoxCore', 'Himil'),
('7mRN2br0', 'Native', 'Leadership of the formation has been given to {HERO_NAME}.'),
('7MU008BT', 'Native', 'F11'),
('7MWaMaez', 'Native', 'Here''s what we''ve got: {ITEM_LIST}. Take them, but let us live.'),
('7N0IliZB', 'SandBox', '{!}quick battle scene 4'),
('7N5jjxsd', 'SandBox', 'That seems reasonable. I am willing to do this.'),
('7n7V9Va5', 'SandBoxCore', 'Irya'),
('7naLQmq1', 'SandBox', 'You have lost the battle against the mercenaries. You have failed to get rid of them as you promised. Now they’ve turned bandit and are starting to plunder the countryside'),
('7nNi6vnV', 'Native', 'Heroes are niceTODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO_TODO'),
('7NnPxNXZ', 'SandBox', 'Personality Traits'),
('7No7syyO', 'SandBoxCore', 'Penek'),
('7NQjRdQz', 'SandBox', 'I''m sorry. This is too much, too fast. I need time to think.'),
('7nVZgjmn', 'SandBox', 'Desporion'),
('7O8IwMgU', 'SandBox', 'Oh, you''ll need my help all right, if you want to get them back - alive, that is. See, my boys have some pretty specific instructions about what to do if there''s a rescue attempt...'),
('7oJ9gIeT', 'Native', 'Trader does not have enough money.'),
('7p6mbzdo', 'SandBox', 'Tell me your story again.'),
('7PcoCifN', 'SandBox', '{NAME} the Rich'),
('7pH9MzS1', 'SandBox', 'So you pay us to fight? What''s in it for you?'),
('7phSQw5i', 'SandBoxCore', 'Hoe'),
('7phVPcDc', 'Native', 'Sets the quality of shaders. A higher value means better graphical effects.'),
('7Pk3bFPC', 'SandBox', 'Noble Retinues'),
('7poObaCF', 'SandBox', 'Yes, they needed a strong king, like a herd of cattle on a mountain trail needs a herdsman who knows the trail. Herds in the mountains, you see... Sometimes the stubborn old bulls, set in their ways, wander off the trail and lead the others toward a precipice.'),
('7pQ3y21E', 'SandBox', 'Thank you again for all your help.'),
('7QdKwOhY', 'SandBox', 'Fortune favors the bold. With you with us, we will win this war quickly.'),
('7QFCINsI', 'SandBox', 'Every time I''ve fought with a band of my ''countrymen,'' I''ve told them: ''Hold your lines. Stay firm. Fight as the Empires does: as a solid hammer, not a gaggle of goats.'' And every time I have seen them disintegrate into a screaming rush as soon as the arrows start flying, to dash themselves on the enemy''s shields or be cut down by cavalry coming in on the sides.'),
('7qfZbVii', 'SandBox', 'I think I could use a man like you.'),
('7QKjVON8', 'Native', 'Jump'),
('7qPda0SA', 'SandBox', 'One of my relatives has fallen victim to his temper during a quarrel and killed a man from {TARGET_VILLAGE}. We have offered to pay the blood money but the family of the deceased have stubbornly refused it. As it turns out, the deceased is a kin of {TARGET_NOTABLE}, the elderman of the region and now the men of {TARGET_VILLAGE} have sworn to kill my relative.'),
('7Qr1yZhJ', 'SandBox', 'So be it. Come see me again if you want to arrange a new one.');
