('fHKHwvsW', 'Native', 'Bronze Banded Pommel'),
('FHM5GcHW', 'SandBox', 'Good. Then I will tell you what I know. I heard about one other piece.[sp:/Sounds/VO/mainquest/mntemp_q01_09.ogg]'),
