('FjRiPhEI', 'Native', 'Routed Party'),
('FjrLf4LE', 'SandBox', 'Indeed. Good infantry is the backbone of an army.'),
('fjthM3fE', 'SandBox', 'I heard that you have pledged allegiance to our lord, {FIRST_NAME}. Excellent... I am sure that you and I will become very good friends. But remember -- if you betray us, it will be the biggest mistake you will ever make.'),
