('PHe0oco1', 'SandBox', 'You fought your way through the attackers to reach the gates. The defenders open them quickly to let you through. When the gates are safely closed behind you, you take a quick tally only to see you have lost the following: {CASUALTIES}.{OTHER_CASUALTIES}'),
('phhXgKRm', 'SandBox', 'Some resisted. The Karakhergit - you may have heard of them. They still dwell in the steppes but they are outcaste, raided for slaves by the others. My people were the Uvait. We were broken up - some bands were lured into the villages with silver, others were hunted down, defeated, and their sons taken as hostages. '),
