('pHrxeTdc', 'SandBox', 'Prisoners:'),
('PhTv43ve', 'SandBox', 'Ah, yes. At last we meet. You sound like a good woman to know. Let us speak together, from time to time.'),
('PHVJ9fOm', 'SandBox', 'But there was a lord, a customer of mine, who had no honor. And he refused to pay me. And having no honor, he laughed at my insults. He did not pull his blade. He had his men drive me away. I can kill one man but not three at once. So here I am.'),
