('PIu7b9wO', 'SandBox', 'I was born around the time she married her fourth husband. My father, well, he was hanged a few months before that. A couple others were hanged, but mostly they were killed by their own followers. You see, the trick to leading bandits is that you can''t value your life very much. Never back down from a fight or an insult. Sooner or later your luck will run out. Usually sooner.'),
