('r88TwVdE', 'Native', 'The mounted archers are the main striking force of the Khuzait horde. Every tribe in the confederacy is expected to muster its best men when the khan marches to war. They fight with speed, patience and cunning, stinging the enemy force with their arrows until it is sufficiently softened up to move in for the kill. '),
