('r8b5miDE', 'SandBoxCore', 'Guard''s Kettle Over Mail Coif'),
('R8dqZlqB', 'SandBox', 'Militia has a %20 chance to spawn with more experienced troops.'),
('r8ga8i93', 'SandBox', 'I like to fight, so I made it known that I''d fight for anyone if the price is right. Shed a little blood, make a little coin, drink it away, make a little more, all in the cause of justice. Not a bad life, eh?'),
('R8hEAwUZ', 'Native', 'Rough Wrapped Grip'),
